assetProfile.longBusinessSummary: Eagle Industry Co.,Ltd., together with its subsidiaries, manufactures, markets, and sells mechanical seals, special valves, and other sealed products in Japan and internationally. It operates Automotive and Construction Machinery Industries, General Machinery Industry, Semiconductor Industry, Marine Industry, and Aerospace Industry segments. It offers mechanical seals for water pumps; lip seals and control valves for A/C compressors; actuators and various valves for turbo systems; solenoid valves for ATs/CVTs; various valves and metal pulsation dampers for fuel systems and metal pulsation dampers; accumulators for various hydraulic paths; reed valves for exhaust emission controls; solenoid valves for air intake- and exhaust-related systems; suspension accumulators; floating seals for undercarriages; actuators for turbo systems; travel damper accumulator; accumulators for brake and pilot arm hydraulic paths; and hydrogen control valves for fuel cell vehicles. The company also provides multi-spring seals, metal bellows seals, cartridge seals, dry seals for agitators, dry gas seals, and diaphragm couplings for general industry applications; magnetic fluid vacuum seals, rotary joint, and welded metal bellows for semiconductor applications; and oil and water lubricated sturn tube seals, oil lubricated stern tube shaft bearings, and water lubricated rubber bearings for the marine industry applications. In addition, it offers turbo pump, main shaft, gearbox, brush, static, and mechanical seals for aircraft, and rocket and spacecraft equipment applications; bellows accumulators for use in international space station; and deals in image processing products. The company was formerly known as Nihon Sealol Co., Ltd. and changed its name to Eagle Industry Co.,Ltd. in June 1978. Eagle Industry Co.,Ltd. was founded in 1964 and is headquartered in Tokyo, Japan.
